#### Deep learning models

| Model | Accuracy | Precision | Recall | F1 Score | ROC-AUC |
| --- | ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: |
| CNN | 0.8585 | 0.8556 | 0.8585 | 0.8567 | 0.9641 |
