## 8. Final Interpretation

Across all four experiment generations, the clearest pattern is:

- boosting models are consistently the strongest performers on these engineered session features
- deep learning improves when the data foundation improves, but architecture changes alone are not enough
- the biggest practical step forward came with Model4 because it upgraded the training dataset and the experiment organization together

If the project continues beyond Model4, the next most meaningful improvement will likely come from better temporal data realism rather than simply adding more complex sequence architectures.
